item.title: Hamachi (help please)
item.dc:creator: @Newb_2341 Newb 2341
item.description:
@Newb_2341 wrote:

  1. You don’t need to - use 127.0.0.1 or localhost while your server is up - but no.
  2. Plugins for what…
  3. When you open runserver, it says some 0’s then a 4 number sentence - that’s your port. Or, you can go into server.java and search for listenerport… the number is the port.
